    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1199083">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1199083/" class="title-link">把璀璨的历史讲成流水账</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1199083"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/BraveHeart/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1020405-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/BraveHeart/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">以心印心</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-08-25"
      class="main-meta">2007-08-25 08:48:22</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1199083_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  实在受不了，把璀璨的历史讲成流水账，没有深入的分析在特定的历史环境下人物的行为，只是告诉你在什么时间产生了什么事情,简直就是蜻蜓点水一样，比我看过的任何一部明史，清史都要差.

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1199083/#comments">(7回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1199083_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1199083_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评14篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
